data.description: Looking for a move-in ready condo close to everything? Look no further!! This end unit 3-bedroom condo has hardwood floors and tile throughout, and a spacious back patio with brick pavers.  The living room features a gas fireplace with a custom mantle. The kitchen is beautiful with 42" cabinets and granite counters, all appliances convey, including a washer, dryer, and chest freezer in the garage! The patio table and chairs remain too! The HVAC was replaced in 2016. The Condo association maintains all exterior elements of this property, the roof was replaced in 2023. The neighborhood is walkable with sidewalks and just a few minutes from the airport, several grocery stores, restaurants, breweries, and more! The town of Fletcher is situated between Asheville and Hendersonville and has one of the area's best parks (Bill Moore Community Park) just a few minutes drive from this amazing home. Make your appointment today, this one will go quickly.
